### Endpoint de consulta unitária da transaction.
GET {{Api}}/v1/transactions/{{transactionId}}
Authorization: {{access_token}}
Accept: application/json

# GetTransactionResponse
# {
#   transactionId: string,
#   description: string,
#   category: string,
#   type: string,
#   date: datetime,
#   amount: decimal,
#   createdAt: datetime,
# }


### Create transaction
POST {{Api}}/v1/transactions
Authorization: {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "description": "Salário de Maio",
  "type": "Income",
  "category": "Lucro",
  "amount": 5000,
  "date": "2025-05-29T03:00:00.000Z"
}


### Massive create transactions (CSV upload)
POST {{Api}}/v1/transactions/massive-create
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="transactions.csv"
Content-Type: text/csv

<./transactions.csv
--boundary--


### Edit transaction
PUT {{Api}}/v1/transactions/{{transactionId}}
Authorization: {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

# EditTransactionInput
{
  "description": "Salário Atualizado",
  "type": "Income",
  "category": "Lucro",
  "amount": 5200,
  "date": "2025-05-25T03:00:00.000Z"
}


### Delete transaction
DELETE {{Api}}/v1/transactions/{{transactionId}}
Authorization: {{access_token}}
Accept: application/json

